data.title: Selected Writings of Sir Edward Coke, vol. III
data.meta_description: Vol. 3 of a 3 vol. set of The Selected Writings. This volume contains Coke’s speech in Parliament (including the Petition of Right), a number of official acts related to Coke’s career, and other matters.
data.text:
Steve Shepherd (editor)

Sir Edward Coke (author)

Vol. 3 of a 3 vol. set of The Selected Writings. This volume contains Coke’s speech in Parliament (including the Petition of Right), a number of official acts related to Coke’s career, and other matters.
